OL,3,CStarmer to face PMQs after Mandelson
OL,4,Cfiles release lay bare splits in
OL,5,CGovernment
OL,7,FSir Keir Starmer is set to face
OL,8,Fquestions from MPs after thousands of
OL,9,Fnewly released documents exposed
OL,10,Fcracks in his government and raised
OL,11,Fquestions over his use of disappearing
OL,12,Fmessages.
OL,14,FThe Prime Minister's weekly appearance
OL,15,Fin the Commons at Prime Minister's
OL,16,FQuestions will be the first
OL,17,Fopportunity MPs have to grill him
OL,18,Fabout the content of the latest files
OL,19,Frelated to Lord Peter Mandelson's
OL,20,Fappointment as Britain's ambassador to
OL,21,Fthe United States.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/5
