OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1780448626
OL,3,CStarmer to face PMQs after Mandelson
OL,4,Cfiles release lay bare splits in
OL,5,CGovernment
OL,7,FMonday's document dump revealed
OL,8,Fprivate messages between Lord
OL,9,FMandelson and senior ministers in
OL,10,Fwhich they admitted their frustrations
OL,11,Fwith Sir Keir's leadership and the
OL,12,Fheart of government.
OL,14,FIn one WhatsApp exchange between Lord
OL,15,FMandelson and Work and Pensions
OL,16,FSecretary Pat McFadden, the senior
OL,17,Fminister complained every meeting he
OL,18,Fhad was to discuss "who can we tax in
OL,19,Forder to pay benefits to others".
OL,26,@zD@TOU{D@`O]
