OL,3,CStarmer to face PMQs after Mandelson
OL,4,Cfiles release lay bare splits in
OL,5,CGovernment
OL,7,FForeign Secretary Yvette Cooper would
OL,8,Fnot be drawn into saying whether she
OL,9,Fbelieved Sir Keir was a strong and
OL,10,Feffective leader, when asked by
OL,11,Fjournalists about the messages
OL,12,Frevealed by the Mandelson files as she
OL,13,Fvisited China.
OL,15,FDowning Street, meanwhile, revealed
OL,16,Fthe limited number of written messages
OL,17,Fbetween the Prime Minister and Lord
OL,18,FMandelson contained in the files was
OL,19,Fbecause Sir Keir uses disappearing
OL,20,FWhatsApp messages.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/5
