OL,3,CStarmer to face PMQs after Mandelson
OL,4,Cfiles release lay bare splits in
OL,5,CGovernment
OL,7,FThe disappearing messages function on
OL,8,FWhatsApp means that Sir Keir's
OL,9,Fcommunications with Lord Mandelson on
OL,10,Fthat platform have not been preserved.
OL,12,FThe Prime Minister defended his use of
OL,13,Fthe function, telling broadcasters:
OL,14,F"All the messages I hold have been
OL,15,Fpassed over.
OL,17,F"I went through the same process as
OL,18,Feverybody else.
OL,20,F"And many people, not just in
OL,21,Fpolitics, use disappearing messages."
OL,26,@vD@AOUyD@AOU|D@AOU}D@eO]
