PN,30305
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1780448626
OL,3,CStarmer to face PMQs after Mandelson
OL,4,Cfiles release lay bare splits in
OL,5,CGovernment
OL,7,FSir Keir, along with Ms Cooper, sacked
OL,8,FLord Mandelson in September 2025 after
OL,9,Fleaked emails which showed the peer
OL,10,Fsent supportive messages even as late
OL,11,Fpaedophile financier Jeffrey Epstein
OL,12,Ffaced jail for sex offences.
OL,14,FMPs voted earlier this year to force
OL,15,Fthe disclosure of documents relating
OL,16,Fto his time as ambassador.
OL,18,FThe Commons is set to debate the
OL,19,Fsecond tranche of the files on
OL,20,FWednesday afternoon, following Prime
OL,21,FMinister's Questions.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/5
